<div id="c1">
<p>I wrote this largely in one sitting, on my phone, while slowly going insane at the hospital. I&#8217;m amazed at how well it came out.</p>

<p class="posted">posted by <a rel="nofollow" href="../index.html">Aaron Swartz</a>
 on September 27, 2006 <a href="femhosp#c1" rel="bookmark">#</a></p>
