<p>Wow. I saw one intelligent reply from a doctor here, the rest of you are elitist fear mongerers (I love writing garbage like this!).  Anyway, here&#8217;s a good option to avoid the woes of our modern health care system&#8230;DON&#8217;T USE IT!  There are hundreds of millions of people that would kill for their child to be &#8220;traumatized&#8221; by our burn centers, or themselves &#8220;driven up the wall&#8221; by our oncology wards.</p>

<p>You people (I use that term loosely) need to eat more red meat and join the team.  Or, quit your job, move to the Arizona desert, build an earthsip, convert to Christian Science (no doctors or hospitals), and live the dream!  The fact of the matter is this:  We are quickly being overtaken as the &#8220;best&#8221; in just about everything that&#8217;s measurable.  So, look at third world health care and relish in the fact that we will have that in about 40 years along with the decline of our wealth and society.  At that time, all of you can yell &#8220;hooray, no more invasive surgeries in drab, depressing hospitals&#8221; as you brush the flies away from the eyes of your suffering child.  Yay!!!</p>

